<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_135_r1l1">Hılpolten 
<del rend="strikethrough">Fra </del> Menndorffer <expan>Pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_135_r1l2">cʒum Hohenſtein </ab>
</div>
